title: No Knead Tangzhong Hokkaido Milk Bread | #stayhome#withme! (EP174)
description:
Today we are making No Knead Tangzhong Milk Bread!

Tangzhong or Yudane in Japanese is a very popular method to make moist and fluffy bread.

Making a homemade bread is a kind of exercise and aroma therapy at the same time.

Enjoy baking! Stay home with me!

Level ☆☆★
IMPORTANT NOTE: READ THIS BEFORE START BAKING
https://princessbamboo.com/important-note-read-this-before-start-baking/

・Tangzhong
2 tbs bread flour
3 tbs water
3 tbs whole milk

・Bread dough
250g(2 cups) bread flour
4g (1 ts) salt
4g (1 ts) active dry yeast
30 g(2 tbs) sugar
150 ml (3/5 cup) whole milk
1 large egg ※keep 1 tbs for egg wash
50g butter

Oven: 20 ~25 mins 200℃（400℉）

active dry yeast
